## Async Iteration

```python
# Async generator
async def fetch_pages(url: str):
    page = 1
    while True:
        data = await fetch(f"{url}?page={page}")
        if not data:
            break
        yield data
        page += 1

# Async for
async for page in fetch_pages(url):
    process(page)

# Async list comprehension
results = [item async for item in async_iterator]
