```

### Common Issues

| Issue | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| "Event loop is closed" | Running after shutdown | Check loop lifecycle |
| Blocking | Sync I/O in async code | Use async libraries or executor |
| Task never completes | Missing await | Check all coroutine calls |
| Memory leak | Tasks not awaited | Store and await all tasks |

